<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>APICTS Admin Invitation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f7fb;
      color: #1f2933;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827 0%, #1f2937 50%, #ef4444 100%);
      padding: 36px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 36px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .credentials-box {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .credential {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .credential span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .credential strong {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      background: #ef4444;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      transition: background 0.2s ease;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #10b981;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 24px 36px;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>APICTS Admin Access Granted</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= userName %>,</h2>
      <p><strong><%= inviterName %></strong> has created an administrator account for you on the APICTS platform with the <strong><%= assignedRole %></strong> role.</p>
      <p>Use the credentials below to sign in to the admin dashboard. For security purposes, please change your password immediately after your first login.</p>

      <div class="credentials-box">
        <div class="credential">
          <span>Admin Email</span>
          <strong><%= userEmail %></strong>
        </div>
        <div class="credential">
          <span>Temporary Password</span>
          <strong><%= tempPassword %></strong>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-bottom: 28px;">Access the admin dashboard using the button below:</p>

      <p>
        <a class="button" href="<%= siteUrl %>/admin-login" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sign in to APICTS Admin</a>
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 32px;">
        If you were not expecting this access or believe it was sent in error, please contact the APICTS security team immediately.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 40px;">
        Welcome aboard,<br />
        <strong>The APICTS Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      This invitation email was generated automatically. Please do not share your credentials with anyone.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

